8V","reactions":[{"name":"eyes","count":2,"users":["U7B4ZD49X","UBDMG6N2J"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"VFaM"}]},{"client_msg_id":"9c3e5005-d90f-445f-b197-5e1093a4f7d1","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"TS公式対応頼む〜 :pray:","ts":"1600998422.009300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"r74xk"}]},{"client_msg_id":"3fc5448d-02ec-4460-b295-535633df2543","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"Lua で OOP やる場合\n\n```local Sample = {}\n\nfunction Sample.new()\n  local self = setmetatable({}, { __index = Sample })\n  self.prop = true\n  return self\nend\n\nfunction Sample:method()\n  return self.prop\nend\n\nreturn Sample```\n```local Sample = require'sample'\nlocal sample = Sample.new()\nprint(sample:method())```\nみたいな書き方なんですが、この `sample:method()` を呼び出すのを `sample.method()` って書いちゃうと「なんかバグる」みたいになってだるいですｗ","ts":"1600998412.009000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"liSr"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7a72d345-35a6-4802-a1f6-b1702cadd99a","type":"message","user":"U7JL1UKKL","text":"互換性を考えるとうーんとなっている","ts":"1600997776.006400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"US1J"}]},{"client_msg_id":"26f6e7df-a394-4604-8478-b74985699f16","type":"message","user":"U8R597E9H","text":"Lua 、大まかには慣れれば悪くないって感じですがメソッド記法がめんどすぎますね…","ts":"1600996884.005600","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"hee","count":2,"users":["U7B4ZD49X","UL6CFN8NR"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"puj"}]},{"client_msg_id":"3d82acb8-0a2b-4b40-b192-8afa3ae7b34b","type":"message","user":"U9S4G0LJW","text":"速度は正義","ts":"1600995435.004500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"pwb"}]},{"client_msg_id":"df0f9d54-a